name: Fayette City National Bank, to use, v. Samberg, Appellant
name_abbreviation: Fayette City National Bank v. Samberg

judges: Before Frazer, C. J., Simpson, Kephart, Schaffer, Maxey, Drew and Linn, JJ.
parties: Fayette City National Bank, to use, v. Samberg, Appellant.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam,
What we said in U. S. Bank and Trust Co. Case, 311 Pa. 320, is clearly applicable here, and rules this case.
The judgment of the court below is affirmed.
opinions.author: Per Curiam,

Donald M. Higbee, with him E. C. Higbee, of Higbee, Matthews & Lewellyn and J. Olan Yarnell, for appellee.
